			<p><span class="smallcaps"><strong>Poe Ballantine</strong></span> is in search of a publisher for his novel <em>Beauty Is in the Eyes of William Holden</em>. By the time you read this, he will be in Odessa, Texas, or maybe Harrisburg, Pennsylvania, or maybe Great Bend, Kansas.</p><a href="/contributors/poe-ballantine" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
